# Claude Code local state. The git worktrees under .claude/worktrees/ each hold
# a full copy of the monorepo, so uploading them makes Nx see every project
# (wyrdfold, wyrdfold-api, wyrdfold-e2e) "defined in multiple locations" and
# `nx build` fails during the Vercel build. Vercel needs none of this.
.claude
.claude-flow
